== Romanian ==
=== Etymology ===
It is agreed to be from PIE ''*del-'', "to split, carve, cut", but whether it is a substrate word or an early loan from Old Slavonic is disputed. The Romanian word has an Albanian cognate, ''[[daltë]]'' (id.).

===Noun===
'''daltă''' {{f}}, pl. ''[[dălţi]]''
#[[chisel]].

